Oh my god. I finally took the time to watch this and I relate so hard to curling your hair and it's just GONE after a few minutes. Having thick/long hair will do that to you purely due to the weight. My best fix is to do a sort of half-tease so that it stays together at least a little bit.

Also, the baby hairs are eternal. Accept them.
